Class CXXLanguageFrontend

java.lang.Object
de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.LanguageFrontend
de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.cpp.CXXLanguageFrontend
All Implemented Interfaces:
de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.HasDefaultArguments, de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.HasTemplates, de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.LanguageTrait
public class CXXLanguageFrontend
extends LanguageFrontend
implements de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.HasDefaultArguments, de.fraunhofer.aisec.cpg.frontends.HasTemplates
The language frontend for translating CXX languages into the graph. It uses Eclipse CDT to parse the actual source code into an AST.

Frontend for ONE CXX File
